Episodes.Title: Better-Like
Episodes.Plot: Issa crashes on Daniel's couch and tries to save up extra cash. Molly returns from a beach vacation with renewed determination to maintain boundaries in her life.

Episodes.Title: Familiar-Like
Episodes.Plot: Issa gets advice from Kelli about her financial situation and plays wingwoman as Daniel tries to make a music-industry connection.

Episodes.Title: Backwards-Like
Episodes.Plot: Issa is inspired while recruiting at a job fair with Frieda. Later, she treats Daniel to a thank-you dinner as she remains hopeful about their future. Molly starts her dream job at a black-owned law firm.

Episodes.Title: Fresh-Like
Episodes.Plot: Issa tries to let go of cherished mementos; Molly vents to her therapist about work.

Episodes.Title: High-Like
Episodes.Plot: The girls take a weekend trip to celebrate Tiffany. Molly has trouble leaving her obsession with work behind.

Episodes.Title: Ready-Like
Episodes.Plot: Issa needs moral support when her new project proves more complicated than she originally thought. Issa and Kelli press Molly to consider dating someone new. Later, the girls attend Tiffany's baby shower and try to be helpful.

Episodes.Title: Obsessed-Like
Episodes.Plot: Issa tries to concentrate on her business plan, but is driven to distraction. Molly steps out of her comfort zone in her love life.

Episodes.Title: Ghost-Like
Episodes.Plot: After facing numerous obstacles, Issa gets discouraged about her project. Molly helps give Issa a drama-free 30th birthday.
